Abrahamson, Respondent, v. Five Year Benefit Order, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. October 26, 1892.) Appeal from fifth district court. Action by Genese Abrahamson against the Five Year Benefit Order.

Argued before Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

M. L. Harney, for appellant. W. H. Townley, for respondent.

N o opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
